---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`FAQ | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Frequently asked questions about Sincloy Games and our projects" />
		<style>
			main {
				width: 960px;
				max-width: calc(100% - 2em);
				margin: 0 auto;
				padding: 3em 1em;
			}
			.page-title {
				margin-bottom: 0.5em;
			}
			.page-subtitle {
				margin-top: 0;
				color: rgb(var(--gray));
				font-weight: normal;
				font-size: 1.2em;
				margin-bottom: 2em;
			}
			.faq-section {
				margin: 3em 0;
			}
			.section-title {
				font-size: 1.8em;
				margin-bottom: 1em;
				color: rgb(var(--black));
				border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
				padding-bottom: 0.5em;
			}
			.faq-item {
				margin-bottom: 2em;
				border-bottom: 1px solid #f5f5f5;
				padding-bottom: 1.5em;
			}
			.faq-question {
				font-size: 1.2em;
				font-weight: 600;
				margin-bottom: 0.5em;
				color: rgb(var(--accent));
			}
			.faq-answer {
				line-height: 1.6;
				color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
			}
			.faq-answer p {
				margin: 0.8em 0;
			}
			.faq-answer ul, .faq-answer ol {
				margin: 0.8em 0;
				padding-left: 1.5em;
			}
			.faq-answer a {
				color: rgb(var(--accent));
				text-decoration: none;
			}
			.faq-answer a:hover {
				text-decoration: underline;
			}
			.contact-section {
				background-color: #f9f9f9;
				border-radius: 12px;
				padding: 2em;
				margin: 3em 0;
				text-align: center;
			}
			.contact-title {
				margin-top: 0;
			}
			.contact-description {
				max-width: 700px;
				margin: 1em auto;
				line-height: 1.6;
			}
			.email-link {
				color: rgb(var(--accent));
				text-decoration: none;
				font-weight: 500;
			}
			.email-link:hover {
				text-decoration: underline;
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1 class="page-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
			<h2 class="page-subtitle">Find answers to common questions about Sincloy Games and our projects</h2>

			<div class="faq-section">
				<h2 class="section-title">About Sincloy Games</h2>
				
				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3 class="faq-question">What is Sincloy Games?</h3>
					<div class="faq-answer">
						<p>
							Sincloy Games is an independent game development studio founded in 2024. We're dedicated to creating 
							innovative and immersive gaming experiences that push the boundaries of interactive storytelling.
						</p>
						<p>
							Our team brings together diverse talents from across the gaming industry, with experience spanning 
							AAA studios, indie development, and other creative fields.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3 class="faq-question">Where is Sincloy Games based?</h3>
					<div class="faq-answer">
						<p>
							Sincloy Games operates as a distributed team with members working remotely from various locations. 
							Our core team is primarily based in North America and Europe, allowing us to collaborate across time zones.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3 class="faq-question">How large is the Sincloy Games team?</h3>
					<div class="faq-answer">
						<p>
							Our team currently consists of 12 full-time members working across various disciplines including game design, 
							programming, art, narrative, audio, and production. We also collaborate with a network of talented freelancers 
							and specialists who help us bring specific expertise to our projects when needed.
						</p>
						<p>
							You can learn more about our team on our <a href="/team">Team page</a>.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3 class="faq-question">Is Sincloy Games hiring?</h3>
					<div class="faq-answer">
						<p>
							While we don't have specific openings listed at the moment, we're always interested in connecting with talented 
							individuals who are passionate about game development. If you're interested in joining our team, please send your 
							portfolio and resume to <a href="mailto:careers@sincloy.com">careers@sincloy.com</a>.
						</p>
						<p>
							Visit our <a href="/team">Team page</a> for more information about our current hiring interests.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="faq-section">
				<h2 class="section-title">Our Games</h2>
				
				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3 class="faq-question">What games is Sincloy Games currently developing?</h3>
					<div class="faq-answer">
						<p>
							Our primary focus is currently on "Project Nova," a sci-fi RPG with player-driven narratives. We're also in the 
							early concept phase for an atmospheric adventure game. You can find more details about our current projects on 
							our <a href="/games">Games page</a>.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3 class="faq-question">When will your games be released?</h3>
					<div class="faq-answer">
						<p>
							We're currently in the early stages of development for our projects and don't have specific release dates to announce yet. 
							We believe in taking the time necessary to create high-quality experiences rather than rushing to meet arbitrary deadlines.
						</p>
						<p>
							The best way to stay updated on our progress is to follow our <a href="/blog">development blog</a> and 
							subscribe to our newsletter.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3 class="faq-question">What platforms will your games be available on?</h3>
					<div class="faq-answer">
						<p>
							We're initially targeting PC (Steam) for our game releases, with potential console releases to follow. 
							Platform specifics will be announced as we get closer to release dates for each project.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3 class="faq-question">Will there be early access or beta testing opportunities?</h3>
					<div class="faq-answer">
						<p>
							Yes, we plan to involve our community in the development process through early access programs and beta testing 
							phases for our games. These opportunities will be announced on our website, social media channels, and newsletter 
							as they become available.
						</p>
						<p>
							If you're interested in participating in future testing, make sure to follow us on social media and join our newsletter.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="faq-section">
				<h2 class="section-title">Technical Support</h2>
				
				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3 class="faq-question">How can I report a bug or technical issue?</h3>
					<div class="faq-answer">
						<p>
							Once our games are available for testing or release, we'll establish dedicated channels for bug reporting and technical support. 
							In the meantime, you can reach out to us at <a href="mailto:support@sincloy.com">support@sincloy.com</a> with any questions.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3 class="faq-question">What are the system requirements for your games?</h3>
					<div class="faq-answer">
						<p>
							System requirements for our games will be published on each game's page as we get closer to release. 
							We're designing our games with optimization in mind to ensure they can run on a wide range of hardware configurations.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="faq-section">
				<h2 class="section-title">Business Inquiries</h2>
				
				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3 class="faq-question">How can I contact Sincloy Games for business or partnership opportunities?</h3>
					<div class="faq-answer">
						<p>
							For business inquiries, partnership opportunities, or press inquiries, please contact us at 
							<a href="mailto:business@sincloy.com">business@sincloy.com</a>.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3 class="faq-question">Does Sincloy Games offer publishing services for other developers?</h3>
					<div class="faq-answer">
						<p>
							At this time, we're focused on developing our own projects and are not offering publishing services for other developers. 
							However, we're always open to collaboration opportunities with other creative teams.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="faq-item">
					<h3 class="faq-question">Can I use Sincloy Games' assets or content in my own projects?</h3>
					<div class="faq-answer">
						<p>
							All Sincloy Games assets, artwork, and content are protected by copyright and may not be used without explicit permission. 
							If you're interested in licensing or using our content, please contact us at 
							<a href="mailto:legal@sincloy.com">legal@sincloy.com</a> with details about your intended use.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="contact-section">
				<h2 class="contact-title">Didn't Find Your Answer?</h2>
				<p class="contact-description">
					If you have a question that wasn't answered here, feel free to reach out to us directly.
				</p>
				<p>
					Contact us at <a href="mailto:info@sincloy.com" class="email-link">info@sincloy.com</a>
				</p>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
